        <headline>Heat Advisory issued June 8 at 7:22AM PDT until June 10 at 9:00PM PDT by NWS Missoula MT</headline>
        <description>* WHAT...Major risk of heat effects expected.

* WHERE...Lower Hells Canyon/Salmon River Region and
Orofino/Grangeville Region.

* WHEN...From noon Monday to 9 PM PDT Tuesday.

* IMPACTS...This level of heat affects anyone without effective
cooling and/or adequate hydration. Impacts likely in some health
systems, heat-sensitive industries and infrastructure.
</description>
        <instruction>Drink plenty of fluids, stay in an air-conditioned room, stay out of
the sun, and check up on relatives and neighbors.</instruction>
